<p>Right after yearend we acquired The Scott &amp; Fetzer Company of Cleveland for about $320 million. The company has sales of about $700 million derived from 17 businesses, many leaders in their fields. Return on invested capital is good to excellent for most of these businesses.</p>



<p><strong>Here's what we're looking for:</strong></p>

<ol>

